message.body: I'm getting nervous about my poster for tomorrow. I don't think it's very good/innovative. I was wondering if you would like to meet a little earlier, I think there will be a lot to go over. Like maybe 4? That way we can be leisurely?
Sure. Don't be nervous. If you already knew how to do this then we wouldn't be doing the study. :)
:) I can't get there early. I have a meeting that starts at 3 and will probably go until 4:30 or so.
I'm sure it will be fine. I just reached a point where a little feedback could go along way.
Ok. No worries. I'm excited to see it.
